{"tid":1165483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於知道點解共產黨成日講勾結外國勢力","createTime":"2019-05-21T22:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T00:00:54.000Z","uid":31637,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b4ce0304699f534a465e55ac89b5935a4d9977","tid":1165483,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:21:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為共產黨有d咩機密情報證明邊個邊個勾結外國勢力<br />\n原來所謂既勾結外國勢力, 係指你係香港或出國向其他國家政府數臭共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係陳方安生, 李柱銘, 陳浩天, 肥黎佬, 黃之鋒, 梁天琦, 黃台仰等等,有接觸過外國官員既全撚部都算勾結外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n姐係好似悲情城市天水圍入面既其中一個暴力家庭, 發生家底暴力或虐待事件, 被虐待既家庭成員向社工或警察求助, 條友係共產黨班傻撚眼中已經算係勾結杜福界或香港警務處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab0f265926ee09f72cfd1140d75944816ca0ac1","tid":1165483,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:40:22.000Z","msg":"當年都係全靠「外國勢力」扶持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/4ec2d5628535e5dd9ef7983e71c6a7efcf1b6273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F9vo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F4ec2d5628535e5dd9ef7983e71c6a7efcf1b6273.jpg&h=01980f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic7.dwnews.net/20170206/1486362027589815abec589.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic7.dwnews.net%2F20170206%2F1486362027589815abec589.jpg&h=e5f0209c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://slidesplayer.com/slide/11322908/61/images/23/毛泽东首次访苏与斯大林的合影+返回目录.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslidesplayer.com%2Fslide%2F11322908%2F61%2Fimages%2F23%2F%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%AE%BF%E8%8B%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E5%BD%B1%2B%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95.jpg&h=43ec7085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic3.dwnews.net/20170831/150416119759a7adadb6004.jpg\" da